- Open this now.
- Okay.


525
00:49:00.321 --> 00:49:01.572
What could this be?

526
00:49:04.033 --> 00:49:05.368
Oh, my god!

527
00:49:05.451 --> 00:49:06.661
You went back for this?

528
00:49:08.329 --> 00:49:09.372
Min!

529
00:49:09.956 --> 00:49:14.794
- Happy birthday!
- This is so thoughtful. I, I...


530
00:49:15.670 --> 00:49:18.548
Well, you did just say
I'm the best assistant you've ever had...


531
00:49:18.631 --> 00:49:21.926
Forget about me being your boss,
I mean, this is...


532
00:49:25.805 --> 00:49:27.932
This is the nicest gift
I've received in a long time.


533
00:49:29.851 --> 00:49:31.394
Come here. Come here.

534
00:49:31.477 --> 00:49:33.980
Hey guys, Min is a,
an emerging journalist.


535
00:49:34.063 --> 00:49:36.232
- Hank and Susan work for CNN.
- Hi.


536
00:49:36.315 --> 00:49:38.276
- Hi, Min.
- Very good to meet you.


537
00:49:42.613 --> 00:49:43.489
Wang.

538
00:49:56.461 --> 00:49:58.337
Wind speed is 7 km/h at 258 degrees.

539
00:49:58.796 --> 00:50:00.548
Speed at 7.

540
00:50:00.631 --> 00:50:02.258
258.

541
00:50:06.262 --> 00:50:07.221
38!

542
00:50:58.147 --> 00:50:59.148
Fly high!

543
00:51:15.414 --> 00:51:16.332
What's that?

544
00:51:46.112 --> 00:51:47.780
Look at this. Look at this.

545
00:51:49.073 --> 00:51:53.870
"Fu Changjiu has never had
any affiliation with Falun Gong.


546
00:51:53.953 --> 00:51:58.541
Furthermore, our practice vehemently
prohibits killing of any kind."


547
00:51:59.917 --> 00:52:01.544
I told you this was all propaganda!

548
00:52:02.086 --> 00:52:03.963
Of course they would deny his involvement.

549
00:52:04.046 --> 00:52:05.506
Who wants to be associated with murder?

550
00:52:05.590 --> 00:52:08.134
Nobody risks their lives to lie.

551
00:52:08.718 --> 00:52:10.386
We've got to talk to this guy.

552
00:52:10.803 --> 00:52:11.804
What are you gonna do?

553
00:52:12.305 --> 00:52:14.181
Walk into the prison
and demand to see him?


554
00:52:16.100 --> 00:52:16.976
No.

555
00:52:17.476 --> 00:52:18.311
I'm not.

556
00:52:20.313 --> 00:52:23.274
THE WHOLE NATION IS
AGAINST HERETICAL RELIGIONS


557
00:52:24.275 --> 00:52:27.445
We're very impressed
with your efforts, Secretary Yang.


558
00:52:28.070 --> 00:52:31.032
We feared you were up against too much.

559
00:52:31.115 --> 00:52:33.034
I'm glad you proved us wrong.

560
00:52:33.534 --> 00:52:35.745
Thank you, leaders, for your trust.

561
00:52:40.458 --> 00:52:43.085
Excuse me, but there are
Falun Gong flyers falling from the sky.


562
00:53:21.374 --> 00:53:23.250
- Relative's name?
- Fu Changjiu.


563
00:53:28.923 --> 00:53:30.967
Fu was executed.

564
00:53:31.050 --> 00:53:33.177
- What?
- No one contacted you?


565
00:53:34.637 --> 00:53:36.347
I thought he was given fifteen years?

566
00:53:36.430 --> 00:53:37.890
There was probably a retrial.

567
00:53:45.606 --> 00:53:46.691
Get Zhu.

568
00:53:47.733 --> 00:53:48.651
Yes, sir.

569
00:53:51.195 --> 00:53:54.323
Director Zhu,
he needs to see you right away.


570
00:53:55.199 --> 00:53:56.742
Yes.

571
00:55:18.908 --> 00:55:21.535
January 23, 2001,

572
00:55:21.619 --> 00:55:23.537
is the Chinese New Year's Eve.

573
00:55:24.246 --> 00:55:28.667
Two self-immolations occurred
near the People's Heroes Monument.


574
00:55:29.210 --> 00:55:32.088
One person died at the scene
and four people were burned.


575
00:55:32.171 --> 00:55:37.384
Two others were stopped by police.

576
00:55:37.468 --> 00:55:40.262
They are all Falun Gong
practitioners from Kaifeng city.


577
00:55:41.597 --> 00:55:45.518
The person who died is Liu Chunling.
In order to ascend to heaven,


578
00:55:45.601 --> 00:55:49.146
they were willing to give up their lives.

579
00:55:49.230 --> 00:55:50.606
It's nonsense!

580
00:55:52.274 --> 00:55:54.777
All that work we did,
trying to change people's minds?


581
00:55:56.529 --> 00:55:58.781
What is going on?

582
00:55:58.864 --> 00:56:00.241
You wouldn't be doing this.

583
00:56:00.324 --> 00:56:03.202
Mom, suicide is a sin.

584
00:56:03.285 --> 00:56:04.995
How can you believe this?

585
00:56:07.623 --> 00:56:09.250
Who are they?

586
00:56:09.333 --> 00:56:11.168
It has been proven that Falun Gong harms

587
00:56:11.252 --> 00:56:12.962
lives and endangers society.

588
00:56:13.045 --> 00:56:16.423
For the sake of people's
peace and society's peace,


589
00:56:16.507 --> 00:56:18.217
It must be resolutely eradicated.

590
00:56:19.051 --> 00:56:20.427
It must be resolutely eradicated...

591
00:56:20.511 --> 00:56:21.929
...resolutely eradicated.

592
00:56:22.680 --> 00:56:26.725
We interviewed the organizer
of the self-immolation, Liu Fang.


593
00:56:26.809 --> 00:56:29.228
The self-immolation
was for ascension to heaven.


594
00:56:29.687 --> 00:56:31.730
Why didn't you light yourself?

595
00:56:31.814 --> 00:56:35.943
As they were burning, I wondered
why they did not ascend to heaven.


596
00:56:36.026 --> 00:56:37.736
Later, I figured it out.

597
00:56:37.820 --> 00:56:40.406
Because their practice hadn't
reached the highest level,


598
00:56:41.657 --> 00:56:44.285
they couldn't ascend.

599
00:56:47.371 --> 00:56:50.749
The Chinese government's ban of Falun Gong

600
00:56:50.833 --> 00:56:53.002
has been warmly embraced
by the general public.


601
00:57:04.889 --> 00:57:06.599
This unit!

602
00:57:12.688 --> 00:57:14.648
Why am I under arrest?
I did nothing wrong...


603
00:57:14.732 --> 00:57:15.983
Shut up. Move it.

604
00:57:16.066 --> 00:57:17.026
Hurry up.

605
00:57:17.109 --> 00:57:18.777
They are Falun Gong.

606
00:57:18.861 --> 00:57:20.487
They deserve it.

607
00:57:45.512 --> 00:57:48.182
The woman who died is from Kaifeng,

608
00:57:48.265 --> 00:57:50.893
a Falun Gong member, named Liu Chunling.

609
00:57:50.976 --> 00:57:53.604
The black smoke rising
from her can be clearly seen


610
00:57:53.687 --> 00:57:55.439
on this footage captured by CNN.

611
00:57:56.440 --> 00:57:58.359
They said they got this footage from CNN.

612
00:57:59.193 --> 00:58:00.444
That's not hard to confirm.

613
00:58:08.285 --> 00:58:10.246
- Daniel?
- Hey, Susan. Congratulations!


614
00:58:10.329 --> 00:58:13.499
That's a hell of a shot Hank got,
I've been watching it on the news all day.


615
00:58:13.582 --> 00:58:14.875
That's not our shot, Daniel.

616
00:58:15.501 --> 00:58:17.378
We were arrested
as soon as the fire began.


617
00:58:17.461 --> 00:58:21.548
We have no idea where it came from.
But no one at CNN shot that footage.


618
00:58:22.091 --> 00:58:24.510
I think they just wanted us
to catch a glimpse.


619
00:58:24.593 --> 00:58:25.594
Just enough

620
00:58:25.678 --> 00:58:28.430
to prove it happened.
Anyway, about to shoot.


621
00:58:28.514 --> 00:58:30.849
- I got to go.
- Okay, yeah. All right, take care.


622
00:58:32.059 --> 00:58:33.269
Who shot the tape?

623
00:58:34.853 --> 00:58:37.314
It's obviously a handheld camera,

624
00:58:37.398 --> 00:58:39.066
close enough to pick up his words.

625
00:58:39.149 --> 00:58:41.694
But how were they right
there when it happened?


626
00:58:42.278 --> 00:58:44.655
Unless they knew it was going to happen.

627
00:58:45.197 --> 00:58:47.324
I think we should be
cautious pushing this, Daniel.


628
00:58:47.408 --> 00:58:49.285
Or even worse, they set it up.

629
00:58:49.952 --> 00:58:51.912
This could mean
that the government is conducting


630
00:58:51.996 --> 00:58:54.081
one of the largest-scale
propaganda campaigns in history.


631
00:58:54.164 --> 00:58:55.374
You just want to ignore it?

632
00:58:56.875 --> 00:58:58.460
What happened
to "standing up for what's right"?


633
00:58:58.544 --> 00:59:01.338
Why are you so adamant
about bringing trouble onto yourself?


634
00:59:04.049 --> 00:59:06.176
People are being hurt,

635
00:59:06.260 --> 00:59:08.304
they're being killed,
they're being jailed.


636
00:59:08.846 --> 00:59:10.889
If we don't act,

637
00:59:10.973 --> 00:59:14.059
if journalism isn't for this,
then what's the point of doing it at all?


638
00:59:14.143 --> 00:59:16.228
But what if you get kicked out again?

639
00:59:16.729 --> 00:59:18.063
What if you never come back?

640
00:59:20.065 --> 00:59:24.653
Sometimes you have to compromise things
you believe in to protect yourself.


641
00:59:29.116 --> 00:59:29.992
Min.

642
00:59:35.456 --> 00:59:36.874
How many times do we need

643
00:59:36.957 --> 00:59:38.334
to go over this, Daniel?

644
00:59:38.417 --> 00:59:42.046
- This is not worth the risk.
- These people,


645
00:59:42.129 --> 00:59:44.882
I cannot sit by
and watch them be manipulated


646
00:59:44.965 --> 00:59:47.051
- into turning against each other...
- Daniel!


647
00:59:47.134 --> 00:59:48.594
Take a deep breath.

648
00:59:48.969 --> 00:59:51.055
Look at this situation logically, okay?

649
00:59:51.138 --> 00:59:53.390
- I...
- You can't blow up your reputation there.


650
00:59:53.474 --> 00:59:55.476
Who could you help
if you get kicked out again?


651
00:59:56.101 --> 00:59:57.227
Be smart, okay?

652
00:59:57.686 --> 01:00:00.397
- What's the smart thing to do here?
- Well, I...


653
01:00:00.481 --> 01:00:02.024
Oh, shit!

654
01:00:02.816 --> 01:00:03.901
Dan.

655
01:00:04.902 --> 01:00:05.778
Are you there?

656
01:00:06.987 --> 01:00:08.489
Oh, God.

657
01:00:08.572 --> 01:00:09.448
Dan.

658
01:00:09.990 --> 01:00:10.866
Did I lose you?

659
01:00:12.826 --> 01:00:15.037
- Dan!
- No, no, I'm still here.


660
01:00:15.662 --> 01:00:17.456
Just thinking.

661
01:00:23.295 --> 01:00:24.463
Sorry, Pat.

662
01:00:24.546 --> 01:00:27.508
I just dropped my favorite teapot.
Damn it.


663
01:00:28.217 --> 01:00:29.385
Hang on a second.

664
01:00:31.053 --> 01:00:32.554
Yeah, you know what?

665
01:00:32.638 --> 01:00:35.891
You're right. I've got

666
01:00:35.974 --> 01:00:39.269
my book to focus on,
and building my career.


667
01:00:39.353 --> 01:00:43.690
What's the point of getting involved
in something I'm not concerned with.


668
01:00:44.024 --> 01:00:45.275
I'm happy to hear that.

669
01:00:45.609 --> 01:00:48.278
Why not take a trip or something?

670
01:00:48.362 --> 01:00:50.114
- Relax.
- Yeah.


671
01:00:51.615 --> 01:00:52.741
Talk later.

672
01:01:25.524 --> 01:01:26.817
What are you looking for?

673
01:01:27.985 --> 01:01:29.528
Invoices, for taxes.

674
01:01:30.487 --> 01:01:31.947
Right where they've always been.

675
01:01:38.871 --> 01:01:39.746
Ha!

676
01:01:41.457 --> 01:01:43.542
You know, I was thinking
about getting out of town.


677
01:01:44.251 --> 01:01:46.587
Maybe visiting some historical cities.

678
01:01:46.670 --> 01:01:47.796
For the book.

679
01:01:48.505 --> 01:01:50.424
That's a good idea. Xi'an?

680
01:01:50.507 --> 01:01:52.468
Lesser known places, maybe.

681
01:01:52.968 --> 01:01:54.136
Ones that aren't written about.

682
01:01:54.928 --> 01:01:57.222
Right. Maybe Luoyang?

683
01:01:57.306 --> 01:02:00.267
It's known as the region
where Chinese civilization originated.


684
01:02:00.350 --> 01:02:01.894
I was hoping for somewhere
known for its food.


685
01:02:01.977 --> 01:02:05.355
- What do you think?
- Of course you are. Maybe Kaifeng?


686
01:02:06.440 --> 01:02:07.774
It's not far from Luoyang.

687
01:02:08.233 --> 01:02:09.735
Two for the price of one.

688
01:02:10.319 --> 01:02:11.153
Sold.

689
01:02:12.029 --> 01:02:13.697
- You'll book the tickets?
- Of course.


690
01:02:35.093 --> 01:02:37.513
You missed your report yesterday.

691
01:02:38.347 --> 01:02:41.058
Nothing important happened,
really, we just...


692
01:02:41.141 --> 01:02:44.436
It's not for you to decide
what is important or not.


693
01:02:46.021 --> 01:02:49.525
Do I need to remind you
what the consequences are?


694
01:02:52.236 --> 01:02:55.864
I'll be charged for being an accomplice

695
01:02:55.948 --> 01:02:57.574
if Daniel endangers national security.

696
01:02:58.992 --> 01:03:00.035
That's right.

697
01:03:01.203 --> 01:03:02.120
So tell me,

698
01:03:03.205 --> 01:03:07.125
what unimportant things happened today?

699
01:03:09.419 --> 01:03:12.422
He left for a trip.
To Luoyang and Kaifeng.


700
01:03:13.632 --> 01:03:15.175
Why Kaifeng?

701
01:03:16.593 --> 01:03:18.136
I suggested it.

702
01:03:18.220 --> 01:03:19.888
He asked for ancient cities.

703
01:03:31.316 --> 01:03:33.110
Send someone to Kaifeng.

704
01:03:37.155 --> 01:03:38.240
Enjoy your meal.

705
01:03:40.284 --> 01:03:41.868
Hi, your meal is ready.

706
01:03:44.830 --> 01:03:46.123
Hello.

707
01:03:46.206 --> 01:03:50.752
I want this, this and this.

708
01:03:50.836 --> 01:03:53.213
These foreigners... Why?

709
01:04:02.222 --> 01:04:03.765
Do you know her?

710
01:04:05.392 --> 01:04:08.228
Yes. Liu Chunling.

711
01:04:08.312 --> 01:04:10.230
She lived nearby.

712
01:04:10.647 --> 01:04:12.274
Had you ever known
her to practice Falun Gong?


713
01:04:12.357 --> 01:04:13.984
No, no.

714
01:04:14.067 --> 01:04:16.111
She is a prostitute in a night club.

715
01:04:16.194 --> 01:04:17.404
Really?

716
01:04:17.487 --> 01:04:18.697
Of course.

717
01:04:18.780 --> 01:04:20.782
You don't believe me? Ask Sun.

718
01:04:20.866 --> 01:04:22.993
They've been neighbors for years.

719
01:04:25.996 --> 01:04:27.706
Ah, Liu Chunling!

720
01:04:28.206 --> 01:04:30.959
She is sick here.

721
01:04:31.043 --> 01:04:33.462
She beats her mother at every turn.

722
01:04:38.425 --> 01:04:40.469
Thank you. Take care.

723
01:04:49.019 --> 01:04:49.895
Stop there.

724
01:04:51.229 --> 01:04:52.898
Play it again, but slow.

725
01:04:56.151 --> 01:04:56.985
There!

726
01:04:57.569 --> 01:04:59.613
- Someone hit her over the head, right?
- Where?


727
01:05:04.743 --> 01:05:05.619
There it is!

728
01:05:07.371 --> 01:05:08.246
Oh, God.

729
01:05:08.330 --> 01:05:10.082
They wanted to make sure she was dead.

730
01:05:15.462 --> 01:05:16.296
Hello?

731
01:05:17.881 --> 01:05:18.757
Where is she?

732
01:05:37.651 --> 01:05:38.985
- Xia...
- You...


733
01:05:40.237 --> 01:05:41.154
...come in.

734
01:06:00.048 --> 01:06:00.966
Thank you.

735
01:06:10.100 --> 01:06:10.976
Xia.

736
01:06:23.864 --> 01:06:24.823
I'm ashamed...

737
01:06:26.116 --> 01:06:27.534
...to be in front of you.

738
01:06:32.706 --> 01:06:35.625
I, I told them everything.

739
01:06:40.964 --> 01:06:45.886
But, but I have to tell you
something very important.


740
01:06:53.435 --> 01:06:56.229
The Tiananmen self-immolation is fake.

741
01:06:56.313 --> 01:06:57.814
What? How do you know?

742
01:06:59.524 --> 01:07:02.068
Remember Liu Fang,
the so-called organizer?


743
01:07:03.153 --> 01:07:04.529
I saw him in the detention center.

744
01:07:05.947 --> 01:07:07.282
What's going on?

745
01:07:09.701 --> 01:07:14.164
We were forced to watch
the video over and over.


746
01:07:14.915 --> 01:07:16.041
I swear I could recite it.

747
01:07:17.125 --> 01:07:21.379
I was working, one day...

748
01:07:22.255 --> 01:07:24.883
Don't worry, Liu.

749
01:07:24.966 --> 01:07:27.594
You'll be bailed out soon enough.

750
01:07:30.472 --> 01:07:32.724
Whatever the Party wants.

751
01:07:34.643 --> 01:07:37.896
You've done your country a great service.

752
01:07:38.438 --> 01:07:41.775
Where did you find them, anyway?

753
01:07:42.234 --> 01:07:45.487
You know I can't talk about that.

754
01:07:45.570 --> 01:07:47.364
Of course.

755
01:07:47.447 --> 01:07:48.907
Let's have a smoke.

756
01:07:53.328 --> 01:07:57.415
Liu, what a bold plan. Incredible.

757
01:07:57.499 --> 01:08:00.126
Isn't this proof?

758
01:08:01.378 --> 01:08:02.838
It's not enough.

759
01:08:04.047 --> 01:08:05.340
But it's a start.

760
01:08:11.263 --> 01:08:12.389
Xia,

761
01:08:14.641 --> 01:08:18.228
Would you be willing
to talk to a reporter?


762
01:08:21.481 --> 01:08:22.482
Yes.

763
01:08:25.402 --> 01:08:26.820
But who dares to expose this?

764
01:08:28.780 --> 01:08:29.823
I might know someone.

765
01:08:32.200 --> 01:08:34.411
- How was the trip?
- It was wonderful.


766
01:08:42.544 --> 01:08:43.879
You were...

767
01:08:45.714 --> 01:08:48.300
You were right about the food.

768
01:08:48.967 --> 01:08:50.343
Was it worth the journey?

769
01:08:52.762 --> 01:08:54.306
Yeah, it was...

770
01:08:55.682 --> 01:08:56.600
...well worth it.

771
01:11:58.531 --> 01:11:59.699
What are you doing?

772
01:12:02.952 --> 01:12:03.828
Uh...

773
01:12:04.329 --> 01:12:05.288
Homework.

774
01:12:05.830 --> 01:12:08.625
Tsinghua University? Impressive.

775
01:12:08.708 --> 01:12:09.918
What are you studying?

776
01:12:10.001 --> 01:12:11.211
City planning.

777
01:12:12.003 --> 01:12:12.921
Continue with your studies then.

778
01:12:14.547 --> 01:12:15.507
All done for today, actually!

779
01:12:18.802 --> 01:12:19.886
Watch it!

780
01:12:20.720 --> 01:12:22.931
Falun Gong! This man is Falun Gong!

781
01:12:40.573 --> 01:12:42.617
Wang! Jun was arrested!

782
01:12:42.700 --> 01:12:44.577
- What?
- Pack up!


783
01:12:57.132 --> 01:12:59.300
- Get the diapers!
- Okay.


784
01:13:06.766 --> 01:13:07.642
Hurry!

785
01:13:29.414 --> 01:13:32.458
NO FALUN GONG

786
01:14:10.705 --> 01:14:11.789
Sit down and rest for a bit.

787
01:14:23.843 --> 01:14:26.095
I know. You're hungry.

788
01:14:26.179 --> 01:14:27.472
It's almost ready.

789
01:14:29.682 --> 01:14:31.351
It's okay. Don't cry.

790
01:14:31.434 --> 01:14:33.186
The bottle is almost ready.

791
01:14:36.856 --> 01:14:39.651
It's okay. Don't cry. 
The bottle's here.

792
01:14:51.329 --> 01:14:52.622
Can you find the diapers?

793
01:14:57.877 --> 01:14:59.212
Oh, no. I forgot them.

794
01:14:59.295 --> 01:15:01.923
I've specifically told you
to bring the diapers!


795
01:15:02.006 --> 01:15:03.925
I panicked. I forgot.

796
01:15:04.008 --> 01:15:06.511
How come you didn't forget
that garbage for your detector?


797
01:15:07.345 --> 01:15:09.472
We need this for tomorrow,
it's integral to the plan.


798
01:15:09.555 --> 01:15:11.307
You still want to go tomorrow?

799
01:15:12.225 --> 01:15:14.936
Finally there's a foreign reporter
interested in our story.


800
01:15:15.436 --> 01:15:17.063
This could change everything!

801
01:15:17.146 --> 01:15:18.231
How can we give up?

802
01:15:18.314 --> 01:15:19.899
What if you're arrested too?

803
01:15:20.942 --> 01:15:22.110
What about our baby?

804
01:15:23.194 --> 01:15:24.279
What about me?

805
01:15:31.869 --> 01:15:32.996
Li

806
01:15:33.579 --> 01:15:34.497
Tell me.

807
01:15:53.266 --> 01:15:54.142
Wang.

808
01:15:55.560 --> 01:15:57.687
You need to make a choice. Right now.

809
01:16:00.148 --> 01:16:01.566
Do you want me and the baby...

810
01:16:03.860 --> 01:16:05.737
...or do you want to go tomorrow?

811
01:16:08.239 --> 01:16:11.784
Li, please don't do this.

812
01:16:26.841 --> 01:16:28.593
It's late. Where are you going?

813
01:16:29.302 --> 01:16:30.219
Li.

814
01:16:30.678 --> 01:16:32.638
Where are you going?

815
01:16:34.015 --> 01:16:34.932
Li.

816
01:16:36.225 --> 01:16:38.853
Li, let's go back and talk.

817
01:16:39.312 --> 01:16:40.938
Where are you going with the baby?

818
01:16:41.439 --> 01:16:42.315
Li!

819
01:16:43.900 --> 01:16:46.361
- Li.
- Stop the car! Stop the car!


820
01:16:47.362 --> 01:16:49.614
Will you just listen to me?

821
01:16:50.281 --> 01:16:51.908
Li. Li.

822
01:16:52.533 --> 01:16:53.368
Li!

823
01:17:11.386 --> 01:17:13.262
How busy you are.

824
01:17:14.138 --> 01:17:16.933
Tell me, where's Wang?

825
01:17:18.309 --> 01:17:19.894
What are you up to?

826
01:17:34.492 --> 01:17:35.827
Tell me.

827
01:17:37.620 --> 01:17:39.872
What exactly is your plan?

828
01:18:10.653 --> 01:18:12.488
Last chance.

829
01:18:50.943 --> 01:18:52.403
I shouldn't have let him go.

830
01:18:53.571 --> 01:18:54.655
It's not your fault.

831
01:18:55.907 --> 01:18:57.492
If I went that day,

832
01:18:57.575 --> 01:18:59.035
Jun wouldn't have been arrested.

833
01:19:00.828 --> 01:19:04.248
Those police killed him, not you.

834
01:19:04.749 --> 01:19:07.502
But he died.
Nothing we do will bring him back.


835
01:19:18.971 --> 01:19:22.767
They killed Jun...

836
01:19:24.644 --> 01:19:28.648
...because he didn't tell them the plan.

837
01:19:30.274 --> 01:19:31.275
Wang.

838
01:19:33.611 --> 01:19:34.946
Wang.

839
01:19:36.781 --> 01:19:38.157
Wang!

840
01:19:42.703 --> 01:19:44.205
He wanted us to proceed.

841
01:19:45.289 --> 01:19:47.542
Do you want him to die for nothing?

842
01:19:51.629 --> 01:19:52.588
No.

843
01:19:54.298 --> 01:19:56.300
I can't allow them to take you back.

844
01:19:59.095 --> 01:20:00.680
You've suffered enough.

845
01:20:16.070 --> 01:20:17.321
Let me tell you something.

846
01:20:18.990 --> 01:20:20.283
They tortured me...

847
01:20:22.326 --> 01:20:24.078
...in all kinds of ways in prison.

848
01:20:30.418 --> 01:20:32.628
Countless times,
I thought about hitting my head


849
01:20:32.712 --> 01:20:34.714
against the wall and ending it all.

850
01:20:40.761 --> 01:20:42.763
But I told myself to hold on.

851
01:20:42.847 --> 01:20:44.307
I must get out of here alive.

852
01:20:46.267 --> 01:20:49.437
I must expose their crimes to the world.

853
01:20:52.148 --> 01:20:53.482
Now I'm out.

854
01:20:54.442 --> 01:20:56.193
But many people are still locked inside.

855
01:20:59.864 --> 01:21:02.950
I will go tomorrow,

856
01:21:04.994 --> 01:21:06.203
even if it's by myself.

857
01:21:33.731 --> 01:21:37.360
Passengers for train E-13

858
01:21:37.443 --> 01:21:42.448
to Shanghai,
please go aboard at platform...


859
01:21:44.408 --> 01:21:49.872
Hi, I was hoping to get a plumber
sent to my apartment as soon as possible.


860
01:21:53.417 --> 01:21:54.251
Great.

861
01:21:55.127 --> 01:21:57.254
Okay. Yes.

862
01:21:58.047 --> 01:21:59.215
I can meet you there.

863
01:22:01.634 --> 01:22:03.678
Okay. Thanks.

864
01:22:16.357 --> 01:22:18.150
I have to go meet a plumber.

865
01:22:18.567 --> 01:22:19.527
See you tomorrow!

866
01:22:45.803 --> 01:22:48.013
- Hey, you the plumbers?
- Yes.


867
01:22:48.097 --> 01:22:49.890
Thanks for coming on such short notice.

868
01:22:49.974 --> 01:22:51.892
Sorry in advance. 
It's a really big job.

869
01:22:51.976 --> 01:22:53.394
It's right up here.

870
01:23:07.324 --> 01:23:10.995
I was having trouble flushing it.

871
01:23:11.704 --> 01:23:14.957
A few days ago.
And now it's completely broken.


872
01:23:16.876 --> 01:23:18.961
- Looks like a big job.
- Yeah.


873
01:23:19.962 --> 01:23:21.297
How long do you think it will take?

874
01:23:21.964 --> 01:23:23.382
A few hours, probably.

875
01:23:24.675 --> 01:23:27.178
- All right, well, you better get started.
- Okay.


876
01:24:01.337 --> 01:24:03.672
- Okay. Hi.
- Hi.


877
01:24:03.756 --> 01:24:06.091
I want you to tell me everything

878
01:24:06.175 --> 01:24:08.677
about the confession
you overheard in prison.


879
01:24:08.761 --> 01:24:11.764
Okay? It might be hard.
But the details are important.


880
01:24:19.104 --> 01:24:20.856
He's really just getting his toilet fixed.

881
01:24:21.232 --> 01:24:22.775
This tip is a bust.

882
01:24:28.447 --> 01:24:30.741
They tortured me so many times.

883
01:24:33.786 --> 01:24:35.120
One day...

884
01:24:36.705 --> 01:24:39.124
...they took off all of my clothes,

885
01:24:40.376 --> 01:24:42.461
and threw me into a men's cell

886
01:24:44.380 --> 01:24:45.214
until morning.

887
01:24:58.310 --> 01:25:00.521
Is there anything else you want to add?

888
01:25:02.523 --> 01:25:06.527
I would like to use my real name
to add credibility.


889
01:25:07.111 --> 01:25:09.572
Okay. All right. I...

890
01:25:10.906 --> 01:25:13.617
I have arranged
for you to leave China tomorrow.


891
01:25:15.119 --> 01:25:18.414
No, no, I want to stay.

892
01:25:20.207 --> 01:25:21.166
For change.

893
01:25:21.750 --> 01:25:24.587
Are you sure? That's a big risk.

894
01:25:33.178 --> 01:25:34.054
Wait a second.

895
01:25:35.556 --> 01:25:36.849
How come there's a baby crying?

896
01:25:43.105 --> 01:25:45.065
We gotta go! We gotta go!

897
01:25:45.149 --> 01:25:46.275
We gotta go now!

898
01:25:46.358 --> 01:25:48.569
- Daniel, the tape recorder.
- Why?


899
01:25:48.652 --> 01:25:50.446
- Do you have a cable?
- Yes.


900
01:25:50.988 --> 01:25:52.448
It'll make them think
we're still in the apartment.


901
01:25:52.531 --> 01:25:54.408
- Okay.
- Shut down the elevators!


902
01:25:56.702 --> 01:25:57.620
Here.

903
01:26:05.461 --> 01:26:07.004
Come on, come on, come on.

904
01:26:12.843 --> 01:26:13.802
Okay, let's go.

905
01:26:18.599 --> 01:26:19.433
Hurry up!

906
01:26:19.516 --> 01:26:21.060
They are still in the apartment!

907
01:26:58.097 --> 01:26:59.348
See...

908
01:27:00.140 --> 01:27:02.184
- This is where we keep the hose...
- Yeah.


909
01:27:02.267 --> 01:27:04.228
- And you get...
- Yeah.


910
01:27:10.067 --> 01:27:10.985
Let me check.

911
01:27:16.281 --> 01:27:17.700
Okay, it's clear. Let's go.

912
01:27:32.214 --> 01:27:33.507
No sign of the target.

913
01:27:34.216 --> 01:27:35.134
No, no way.

914
01:27:35.217 --> 01:27:36.969
Okay, there's a,
there's a back door, come on.


915
01:27:43.058 --> 01:27:44.685
No, we're stuck.

916
01:27:47.604 --> 01:27:48.564
Wait right here.

917
01:27:50.190 --> 01:27:52.526
Until you hear them pass.
Then go for the back door.


918
01:27:52.609 --> 01:27:53.694
Wait, wait, wait, wait...

919
01:27:53.777 --> 01:27:56.113
Get out of China! 
As soon as possible.

920
01:27:57.448 --> 01:27:58.449
Get down.

921
01:28:02.995 --> 01:28:03.996
Stop!

922
01:28:41.909 --> 01:28:44.787
Where is Daniel Davis?

923
01:28:57.382 --> 01:29:00.761
WANTED 
- NATIONAL ALERT FOR DANIEL DAVIS

924
01:29:10.646 --> 01:29:11.814
Have you seen this person?

925
01:29:18.320 --> 01:29:19.154
Where is he?

926
01:29:19.947 --> 01:29:22.574
Sir, I really don't know.

927
01:29:23.450 --> 01:29:25.077
I have already given
all of the information.


928
01:29:25.577 --> 01:29:27.371
You were very close.

929
01:29:28.122 --> 01:29:29.623
The two of you.

930
01:29:29.706 --> 01:29:32.626
It's hard to believe that he would leave
without telling you where he was going.


931
01:29:32.709 --> 01:29:34.962
He was my boss, nothing more.

932
01:29:35.796 --> 01:29:38.924
I swear to you.
He left the office to run an errand


933
01:29:39.007 --> 01:29:40.759
and that was the
last time I saw him.

934
01:29:44.847 --> 01:29:46.807
I, I really don't know where he is.

935
01:29:48.725 --> 01:29:51.436
It would be
in your best interest to find out.


936
01:29:52.479 --> 01:29:53.480
Don't you think?

937
01:30:02.906 --> 01:30:05.242
If you find Daniel,
what will happen to him?


938
01:30:08.078 --> 01:30:10.080
What you should be asking me is,

939
01:30:10.622 --> 01:30:12.207
what will happen to you...

940
01:30:14.459 --> 01:30:15.919
...if he gets away?

941
01:30:26.638 --> 01:30:27.639
What are you doing?

942
01:30:58.837 --> 01:31:02.382
You are not a weak man, Wang.

943
01:31:04.384 --> 01:31:06.386
You have done everything you could.

944
01:31:08.180 --> 01:31:11.767
One needs to know
when to retreat to fight another day.


945
01:31:13.727 --> 01:31:18.815
Do you really think an article
by a foreigner can save Falun Gong?


946
01:31:24.947 --> 01:31:27.991
Tell me where Daniel is.

947
01:31:29.701 --> 01:31:31.370
You stay alive.

948
01:31:31.995 --> 01:31:35.916
And someday you'll get
to hear your child call you "Dad."


949
01:31:42.130 --> 01:31:45.801
At least my child will grow up

950
01:31:47.344 --> 01:31:50.847
knowing that her father

951
01:31:51.765 --> 01:31:53.517
fought for the truth.

952
01:31:54.935 --> 01:31:55.811
The truth?

953
01:32:02.442 --> 01:32:04.027
From what, your little flyers?

954
01:32:05.654 --> 01:32:08.365
There are more than two thousand
newspapers nationwide,


955
01:32:08.448 --> 01:32:10.284
circulating to millions every day.

956
01:32:12.744 --> 01:32:14.371
How many flyers do
you really think you can print?


957
01:32:18.166 --> 01:32:19.209
One day,

958
01:32:20.210 --> 01:32:22.212
the lies will be
seen for what they are.

959
01:32:24.464 --> 01:32:26.049
In the face of the truth,

960
01:32:27.384 --> 01:32:30.220
no matter what misinformation you spread,
people will see through it.


961
01:32:32.097 --> 01:32:37.728
Even your military
and police may turn against you.


962
01:32:39.855 --> 01:32:42.357
Did it ever occur to you?

963
01:32:45.777 --> 01:32:46.820
Interesting.

964
01:32:52.284 --> 01:32:53.702
I have a question, though.

965
01:32:55.620 --> 01:32:58.540
Do you think you'll
get to see that day?

966
01:32:59.333 --> 01:33:00.876
Ask yourself.

967
01:33:02.586 --> 01:33:08.258
You are an evil
person in an evil machine.

968
01:33:09.593 --> 01:33:13.930
You'll either be destroyed
by power struggles in the Party,


969
01:33:15.057 --> 01:33:17.476
or be brought to justice
when the Party eventually falls.


970
01:33:19.436 --> 01:33:25.692
What use will the money
and the power be, then?


971
01:33:29.988 --> 01:33:33.492
Everyone is a victim

972
01:33:34.159 --> 01:33:36.370
in a society with no truth or justice.

973
01:33:37.579 --> 01:33:39.081
And you are no exception.

974
01:34:09.069 --> 01:34:10.237
Enjoy.

975
01:34:23.083 --> 01:34:24.000
The car is here.

976
01:34:34.886 --> 01:34:36.179
It's time to go.

977
01:34:41.393 --> 01:34:43.562
Thank you. Thank you.

978
01:36:08.772 --> 01:36:09.856
Thank you.

979
01:37:13.169 --> 01:37:14.879
Despite the spread of information

980
01:37:14.963 --> 01:37:18.216
to the Western world, persecution in China

981
01:37:18.300 --> 01:37:20.510
continues to this day.

982
01:37:22.596 --> 01:37:23.513
In fact...

983
01:37:24.723 --> 01:37:29.936
...one of the key sources
for this article is in prison,


984
01:37:30.854 --> 01:37:32.814
presumably being tortured,

985
01:37:34.107 --> 01:37:35.275
as I speak to you now.

986
01:37:36.651 --> 01:37:37.527
His name...

987
01:37:38.778 --> 01:37:40.655
...is Wang Boyu.

988
01:37:41.364 --> 01:37:44.492
And more than anyone
I've met on this journey,


989
01:37:44.576 --> 01:37:47.746
he embodied the principles of Falun Gong.

990
01:37:48.330 --> 01:37:49.164
Truth.

991
01:37:50.123 --> 01:37:51.249
Compassion.

992
01:37:52.751 --> 01:37:53.835
Tolerance.

993
01:37:54.961 --> 01:37:56.880
He risked everything for them.

994
01:37:59.799 --> 01:38:02.761
I only hope we will do the same.

995
01:38:03.678 --> 01:38:07.349
Now, there have been some concerns

996
01:38:07.432 --> 01:38:10.852
raised by Western countries.

997
01:38:11.561 --> 01:38:16.983
But little has been done
to protect these innocent people.


998
01:38:18.401 --> 01:38:20.028
We must be more like Wang.

999
01:38:21.821 --> 01:38:24.824
We must do everything we can

1000
01:38:26.242 --> 01:38:28.244
to bring the truth into the light.

1001
01:38:29.537 --> 01:38:30.413
Thank you!

1002
01:38:32.874 --> 01:38:33.708
Thank you.

1003
01:38:36.461 --> 01:38:37.337
Thank you.

1004
01:38:49.349 --> 01:38:51.184
Attention please,

1005
01:38:51.267 --> 01:38:56.439
train number E-13 from Beijing

1006
01:38:56.523 --> 01:39:00.193
has arrived at Shanghai station.

1007
01:39:19.337 --> 01:39:20.213
Well, you won.

1008
01:39:28.596 --> 01:39:34.561
We'll get a few diplomatic letters
of concern, perhaps.


1009
01:39:39.107 --> 01:39:40.066
Then, what?

1010
01:39:42.652 --> 01:39:44.779
Soon you'll be executed in secret.

1011
01:39:47.157 --> 01:39:48.616
And the world will forget.

1012
01:39:49.909 --> 01:39:52.203
They'll forget this article.

1013
01:39:52.787 --> 01:39:53.913
And you.

1014
01:39:56.082 --> 01:39:57.584
And soon they'll forget
Falun Gong altogether.


1015
01:40:14.893 --> 01:40:15.894
I see.

1016
01:40:26.571 --> 01:40:27.614
Enjoy

1017
01:40:29.282 --> 01:40:30.575
your last meal.

1018
01:41:08.196 --> 01:41:10.573
Secretary Yang! 
Secretary Yang!

1019
01:43:20.912 --> 01:43:22.455
Perhaps due to international pressure,

1020
01:43:22.538 --> 01:43:24.874
I was eventually sentenced
to 8 years in prison.


1021
01:43:26.542 --> 01:43:29.504
Those 8 years are supposed
to be the prime of one's life.


1022
01:43:30.630 --> 01:43:35.051
But for me it was a nightmare
I'd rather not remember.


1023
01:43:37.053 --> 01:43:41.849
After I was released, my family
and I managed to find refuge in the U.S.


1024
01:43:44.018 --> 01:43:47.313
However, many practitioners
I know are still persecuted in China.


1025
01:43:49.440 --> 01:43:53.987
Many religious groups, ethnic minorities

1026
01:43:54.070 --> 01:43:57.865
and political dissidents
are still suppressed.


1027
01:43:59.701 --> 01:44:04.247
The Chinese regime still lies
to its own people and to the whole world.


1028
01:44:06.457 --> 01:44:09.752
I believe that no matter
how powerful lies are,


1029
01:44:09.836 --> 01:44:12.005
if we all seek the truth,

1030
01:44:12.463 --> 01:44:15.008
insist on the truth and tell the truth,

1031
01:44:16.175 --> 01:44:18.511
truth will ultimately prevail.